de: Amendment No. 2 to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the Government of the Republic of Indonesia on the granting of technical assistance for "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"  - 18-04-2019 - Verständigungsprotokoll zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und der Republik Indonesien betreffend "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"
en: Amendment No. 2 to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the Government of the Republic of Indonesia on the granting of technical assistance for "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"  - 18-04-2019 - Memorandum of Understanding between the Ministry of Public Works of the Republic of Indonesia and the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) of the Swiss Confederation on the granting of technical assistance for "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"
fr: Amendment No. 2 to the Memorandum of Understanding between the Government of the Swiss Confederation and the Government of the Republic of Indonesia on the granting of technical assistance for "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"  - 18-04-2019 - Protocole d'entente entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO et la République d'Indonésie concernant "Emission Reduction in Cities - Solid Waste Management Programme"
